release_note: 1. Added vertical page turning function which makes writing page by page smoother. 2. Added positive timing 3. Page jump optimization and more accurate positioning 4. The square frame after taking the photo is removed and the photo will not be cropped. 5. After taking a screenshot with the screenshot pen you can also drag and add it to the page by long pressing the pen. 6. Fixed some other bugs
Fixed the image loss problem that occurred when upgrading the old version to version 3.4.0 or 3.5.0.

1. Added backup and recovery function to restore notes to historical versions 2. Support keyboard shortcuts 3. You can create text boxes with your hands. Select the text box pen and click with your hands. 4. The database adds real questions for the fourth and eighth majors in English. 5. Demonstration pen and disappearing pen newly available in a variety of colors 6. Fixed the problem of the disappearing pen being stuck when writing continuously.
New: Note layer function there are three levels each level can be annotated and edited independently and the two levels can be compared and viewed

Hello Welcome to download Notes ! Notes is updated about every two weeks. The basic functions around Apple Pencil have been relatively complete. Now we provide it for everyone to use for free. If you find it useful you are welcome to introduce it to your friends send it to Xiaohongshu and send it to your friends. Circle to help promote Notes . We would like to express our special thanks to the early users of the App especially those who gave us feedback and paid. Thank you very much. In the future we will provide more services around note taking on iPad and strive to be the best note taking app in the world for iPad. We very welcome to contact us for any reason WeChat ID is changyujishu1 This version also adds: Page batch deletion function in the full screen thumbnail state multiple pages can be selected for batch deletion The page order can be adjusted up or down in full screen or left thumbnail state you can long press the page and drag the page to adjust the order Notes Team July 20 2023
